added.title: The Chosen
added.description: When a teenage orphan girl, Iyanu, unknowingly triggers her Divine Powers, she escapes Elu, the last standing city in the known world, and embarks on a remarkable journey to discover the truth about the evil lurking in the realm of Yorubaland.

added.title: The Betrayal
added.description: Elu descends into civil war as Biyi, Oba Adeyinka and Kanfo tell personal stories of past heartbreak. Iyanu, Toye, Ekun and Biyi struggle to reach The Source, while Olori continues her search for Iyanu.

added.title: Ice to Beat You
added.description: A chilling challenge inside an iceberg leads to the coldest elimination of the season.

added.title: Canoe Believe It?
added.description: During a fun-filled day of canoe jousting, a special friendship is founded and an outed cheater gets pounded.

added.title: Fun Fight at the Oh Cake Corral
added.description: It's definitely no cake walk as Campers compete in the ultimate island bake-off. A very special guest judge even stops by for a bite!

added.title: Haulin' n' Ballin'
added.description: The fate of Priya and Caleb's relationship hangs in the balance as Zee struggles to keep a secret. And it all plays out during a brutal game of human pinball.

added.title: Breaking Up Is Hard To Do
added.description: Caleb is desperate to put his relationship with Priya back together while the campers tear apart the largest objects they can find.

added.title: Circling The Drain
added.description: Julia gets between Caleb and Priya during the most painful memory game of all time.

added.title: Working K9 to 5
added.description: Release the hounds! Campers are hunted by a pack of fearsome attack dogs. And one pug.

added.title: Off The Hook
added.description: Things get scary when campers are pulled into a fishhook challenge that pits them against each other AND their worst fears.

added.title: Soar Losers
added.description: Only 3 campers remain and if any of them live through the final challenge they might win the 1 million dollars Chris promised them. But on Total Drama Island promises are a lot like bones; they're often broken.

added.title: Meet the Victims
added.description: Chris welcomes 16 new campers back to the original island and divides them into two teams who face-off in a blindfolded challenge that's sure to cause pain.

added.title: Ranger Norm
added.description: When Tabes leaves for a conference, the Bears have to deal with her substitute, Ranger Norm.

added.title: Shmorby
added.description: The Bears get a Shmorby home assistant device and become lazy couch potatoes.

added.title: Snake Babies
added.description: Charlie adopts baby snakes despite the Bears thinking he's not ready for parenthood.

added.title: Sandcastle
added.description: The Baby Bears build a giant sandcastle. But when some kids declare war on the Bears, they must fight to defend their new home.

added.title: Bros in the City
added.description: The Bears star in a reality TV show along with Griff, Tom, and Isaac.

added.title: Cousin Jon
added.description: When the Bears attend Chloe's family reunion, they fall victim to the mischievous pranks of Chloe's cousin, Jon.

added.title: Lord of the Poppies
added.description: Grizz and the Poppy Rangers go camping on an island, but they soon find themselves deserted.

added.title: The Mummy's Curse
added.description: The Baby Bears must return a mummy to its tomb or else they'll be cursed forever.

added.title: Band of Outsiders
added.description: A gang of streetwise kids takes Baby Ice Bear under their wing.

added.title: Tabes & Charlie
added.description: Tabes and Charlie team up to find Tabes' missing dog, Kirk.

added.title: Dungeon Doug
added.description: On a trip into the world of Dungeon Doug, Oscar and his dad find themselves on a father-son bonding mission.

added.title: Tub on the Run
added.description: While Hedgehog and Max scour the island in search of a missing tub, everyone is dying to know: are things weird between them?

added.title: Spotted Bear Stretch
added.description: On the eve of the Spotted Bear Stretch, Oscar and his pajamas are stuck at Susie's place as unwelcome house guests.

added.title: French Toasting
added.description: Lucy's suspicious behavior prompts Oscar and Hedgehog to investigate whether or not she's the kingpin of a secret society.

added.title: We'll Just Move the Stars
added.description: When an astrological mismatch threatens King and Puddle's wedding, Oscar and Hedgehog join them on a quest to ensure love conquers all.
